l">提供付费域名服务</a>，作为用户验证身份的一种方式。目前尚不清楚该应用程序何时向公众开放，经核实，一些代码仍在 eBay 上以数百美元的价格出售。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>另一方面，Meta 从一开始就选择让所有人都可以使用 Threads，尽管它仍然缺乏一些关键功能。 Threads 在 7 月份推出仅一周后就<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/metas-threads-races-to-100-million-users-in-under-a-week-070740016.html">拥有了 1 亿用户</a>，但<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:6;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/you-can-now-search-threads-for-signs-of-life-193007064.html?_fsig=4aFTQxm4_SRttUiaasoiEQ--%7EA" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/you-can-now-search-threads-for-signs-of-life-193007064.html?_fsig=4aFTQxm4_SRttUiaasoiEQ--%7EA">关键字搜索</a>本月初才开始推出。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/twitter-spinoff-bluesky-hits-1-million-users-063355343.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/twitter-spinoff-bluesky-hits-1-million-users-063355343.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 951252a6-6940-43a1-a173-4069e027b449</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 13 Sep 2023 06:33:55 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694586815</ingested><modified> 2023-09-13T06:33:40+00:00</modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Social & Online Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="4024" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/1c5bb8e0-51f3-11ee-bbd7-11abb433b8a6" width="6048"><media:keywords>标题</media:ke